
                                 auditsyscall-no-oabi
                                  ------

1. Introduction
----------------

The auditsyscall-no-oabi template provides a mechanism to audit system call
on ARM in kernel on the target. According kernel Kconfig, if CONFIG_OABI_COMPAT=y,
Audit System call can not be enabled.


2. Usage
--------

Add this template using the following configure script option.
ie.: --with-template=feature/auditsyscall-no-oabi

This will ensure the required kernel config values are set.


3. Installation
----------------

This template will include audit system call on arm in kernel image.

